Aw Snap!
Zuaro OS has just crashed because of a problem that it could not cope with occured. This can be anything from a failure to a virus infection. Your data is fine and we will prompt if you want your last session to load up again.
If you are seeing this VERY often, then take me to a PC specialist or reinstall Zuaro OS yourself if you`re able to.
